Package: com.victorlobe.icloudmailfix
Name: iCloudMailFix
Version: 1.0.1
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: Restores full iCloud Mail functionality on iOS 6 and later devices. This tweak fixes the compatibility issue with modern iCloud servers by creating a local proxy that handles the connections. See Settings > iCloud Mail Fix for setup instructions.
Maintainer: Victor <victor@victorlobe.me>
Author: Victor <victor@victorlobe.me>
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate, PreferenceLoader, firmware (>= 6.0)
Priority: optional
Compatibility: iOS 6.0+
